reviewText: Not as good as #1, but hey, its FUBAR

I ordered this because it is advertised as having the original Fubar included on it (Fubar I and II.) The product actually only has Fubar II on it. So the description is misleading. You can actually find a much cheaper version of Fubar II on Bluray on Amazon, Target or Walmart so don't buy this version
i find myself saying "give'r" and "all the silk in china couldn't cover that" because of this movie. Awesome find i saw it late night and had to finish it so i bought it. good ol comedy
